        <label>open rift to eldritch planet</label>
        <description>Open a rift to the eldritch planet to cause everyone in the area to immediately become terrified. Whatever exists on the planet is so terrifying that even the Astral Psionist has never laid eyes upon it, for if it is let loose, then this world will probably be lost.</description>
