    <AbilityDef ParentName="SHGPsionicBase">
        <defName>SHG_Psionist_Chaotic</defName>
        <label>open rift to chaotic planet</label>
        <description>Open a rift to the chaotic planet to release a medley of exotic spores that have uncontrollable effects. Unlike the Psychedelic planet, these spores are not solely dedicated to engaging the anger portions of the brain, and the effects of them can vary wildly. There is a chance that they will have no effects at all, or they could have multiple effects on any given individual.</description>
        <iconPath>Psionist/Dimensional/Gene_Psionist_Chaotic</iconPath>
        <writeCombatLog>True</writeCombatLog>
        <statBases>
            <Ability_EntropyGain>100</Ability_EntropyGain>
